profile: Stephen worked for a large Toronto based company for 3+ years leading projects for plastering, re-painting, water damage repair, and more. He wanted to create a more personal connection with the customer, so he started Stephen Fletcher Painting to provide professional and quality work to residential home owners. With 15+ years of experience under his belt, Stephen Fletcher Painting guarantees quality and satisfactory work.
specialities: Popcorn Ceiling Removal, Mirror Finish, Caulking, Wet Sanding (Minimal Dust)
